00:07:17.780 --> 00:07:18.740
<v Speaker 2>Cansada.

00:07:18.740 --> 00:07:19.220
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:07:19.220 --> 00:07:20.580
<v Speaker 1>Estoy cansada.

00:07:20.580 --> 00:07:22.900
<v Speaker 1>So if you want to say I'm tired of

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:25.960
<v Speaker 1>dancing, cooking, cleaning.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:28.600
<v Speaker 1>It's all gonna be with the two form.

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:31.160
