<v Speaker 1>And how do you think form might be in Spanish if you had to guess it?

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:49.840
<v Speaker 2>Forma.

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:50.640
<v Speaker 1>Yes.

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:51.280
<v Speaker 1>Forma.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:51.840
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:54.560
<v Speaker 1>So how would you say a way of doing it?

