00:09:07.639 --> 00:09:10.600
<v Speaker 1>Es una forma de hacerlo good.

00:09:10.520 --> 00:09:16.840
<v Speaker 1>I don't believe in arguing like this in this way.

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:20.680
<v Speaker 1>I don't believe in arguing in this way.

00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:21.000
<v Speaker 1>So

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:30.200
<v Speaker 1>To believe is krer, kreer and it has two E's, C-A-E-E-A, Kraer.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.480
